title: Kendall Jenner Explains Going Braless in Sheer Shirt: 'I Was Having a Really Good Boob Day'
text: Kendall Jenner Explains Going Braless in Sheer Shirt: 'I Was Having a Really Good Boob Day' by Alex Ungerman 2:05   Playing Kendall Jenner Explains Going Braless in Sheer Shirt: 'I Was Having a Really Good Boob Day' Kendall Jenner may be making "good boob day" a thing. The reality star took to her website on Wednesday to explain that racy pizza-emoji braless torso/sheer top pic she shared to Instagram last November. A photo posted by Kendall (@kendalljenner) on Nov 5, 2016 at 8:45pm PDT WATCH: Kendall Jenner Shows Off Star-Shaped Nipple Pasties on Snapchat "I don't know if you can relate, but I just felt like I was having a really good boob day, lol," the 21-year-old wrote. "Do you know what I mean? Your boobs go through phases and on this particular day, I felt like they just looked nice!" "My shirt was see-through, so I took this photo and just texted it to Hailey [Baldwin] and Gigi [Hadid] before I left to meet them and was like, 'Is this too much?'" she continued. "They wrote back, 'It's kind of a lot, but if you're into it, go for it!'" Good to know it was a friend-sourced pic, but that still doesn't explain the food emojis! WATCH: Kendall Jenner and A$AP Rocky Reunite in Paris, the City of Love "As far as the pizza emojis go, when I decided to Instagram the picture, I could've covered my nipples with anything, but I chose them as a little nod to Pizza Boys (the DJ/friend group I'm part of)," Jenner explained. Of course, the Keeping Up With the Kardashians star has nothing to explain, especially because the sheer, nipple-baring look has become a staple of her style.
